{"id":"6422","name":"happy-hour-for-whom-the-bell-tolls","title":"Happy Hour: For Whom The Bell Tolls","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-01-24T18:30:00-06:00","tags":["bank robbery","country music marathon","FBI","lane kiffin","mnps","montgomery gentry","regions bank","silgo bridge","snow","TDOT","titans","usc","winter weather"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/39296163@N08/5375937961/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5208/5375937961_ff17a5db12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\"></a></p><ul><li>It will snow! It won&#x2019;t snow! We&#x2019;re getting 1/2-inch! We&#x2019;re getting threeinchesplus! We&#x2019;re going to get a blizzard! It might actually just rain! Winter storm warning! Winter storm warning canceled! Gosh, okay, can we stop this already? [<a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2011/01/rain-through-tuesday-snow-after-midnight-wednesday-could-be-big/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville WX</a>]</li><li>Metro Police and the FBI are looking for the guy who robbed the Regions Bank downtown this morning. If you have any information, they would like to hear from you. [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/police-fbi-seek-man-who-robbed-downtown-regions-bank?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+%28Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News%29&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li><li>The Titans are really, really trying to sue Lane Kiffin for allegedly luring their players away, but they are now on their third judge because the first two recused themselves. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/sports/26596373/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>A bridge called the Silgo Bridge in East Tennessee is crumbling so badly that TDOT has installed some nets underneath it to catch the falling rock so it doesn&#x2019;t capsize anyone&#x2019;s boat. <a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?client=safari&amp;rls=en&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;q=sligo+bridge&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;hq=sligo+bridge&amp;hnear=sligo+bridge&amp;cid=0,0,17739917639528307411&amp;ei=gRg-TaP2JMrVgQfG_KnrCA&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=local_result&amp;ct=image&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBoQnwIwAA\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;maps.google.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Here is this bridge on the map</a> so that you can never drive over it! [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/26600535/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Some major course changes are in store for the Country Music Marathon this year. Also, Montgomery Gentry will be headlining the post-marathon concert. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13899375\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/39296163@N08/5375937961/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>hikenandhistory</em></a>.</p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}